data.description: Over 2,000 SQFT under AC, Welcome to this absolutely stunning, income-producing 5-bedroom,3-bathroom corner lot pool home with a thoughtfully designed open concept. This property has undergone a complete remodel, featuring spacious bedrooms, vaulted ceilings, and an eye-catching waterfall kitchen with high-quality work and attention to detail. Step outside to your very own outdoor paradise, complete with a refreshing pool anda custom outdoor bar and kitchen equipped with brand-new appliances. With impact windows and doors, this home not only offers a pristine look but also enhances security and energy efficiency. Don't miss the opportunity to make this extraordinary property your own schedule a showing today and ask the agent for Airbnb financials
